Adewunmi Aderemi bụ onye nkuzi basketball ụmụ nwanyị Naijiria
Ọ zụrụ First Bank BC na asọmpi ndị ọkachamara kachasị elu na Naịjirịa, maka oge iri na anọ
Na mba ụwa, Aderemi jere ozi dị ka onye na-enyere ndị otu egwuregwu basketball nke ụmụ nwanyị Naịjirịa aka gụnyere na afọ puku abụọ na isii FIBA World Olympic Qualifying Tournament for Women.
Ọ zụrụ First Bank BC na ọtụtụ FIBA Africa Women's Clubs Champions Cup tupu Peter Ahmedu anọchie ya n'ọnwa Ọktoba afọ puku abụọ iri na ise.
